or: var(--color-text-hyperlink);\">Climb</a> (<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Strength-Str-\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; cursor: pointer; color: var(--color-text-hyperlink);\">Str</a>), <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/fly\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; cursor: pointer; color: var(--color-text-hyperlink);\">Fly (</a><a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Dexterity-Dex-\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; cursor: pointer; color: var(--color-text-hyperlink);\">Dex</a>), <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/perception\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; cursor: pointer; color: var(--color-text-hyperlink);\">Perception</a> (<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Wisdom-Wis-\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; cursor: pointer; color: var(--color-text-hyperlink);\">Wis</a>), <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/stealth\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; cursor: pointer; color: var(--color-text-hyperlink);\">Stealth</a> (<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Dexterity-Dex-\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; cursor: pointer; color: var(--color-text-hyperlink);\">Dex</a>), and <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/swim\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; cursor: pointer; color: var(--color-text-hyperlink);\">Swim</a> (<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Strength-Str-\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; cursor: pointer; color: var(--color-text-hyperlink);\">Str</a>). In addition to these skills, an animal companion with Intelligence score 2 or lower can only have ranks in  <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/escape-artist\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; cursor: pointer; 