/survival\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; cursor: pointer; color: var(--color-text-hyperlink); font-family: Signika, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Survival</a> (<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Wisdom-Wis-\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; cursor: pointer; color: var(--color-text-hyperlink); font-family: Signika, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Wis</a>).</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: Signika, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: Signika, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Skill Ranks per Level</strong>: 2 + <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Intelligence-Int-\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; cursor: pointer; color: var(--color-text-hyperlink);\">Int</a> <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Determine-Bonuses\" style=\"box-sizing: bord